{"tid":219424,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市狂潮】野村：樓市兩個月內見頂","createTime":"2017-04-27T08:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T09:57:53.000Z","uid":24527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6bab3abf029fe552c34790e5fa5a77efa81d35ba","tid":219424,"uid":24527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"【樓市狂潮】野村：樓市兩個月內見頂！<br />\n<br />\n即時財經  2017-04-27 12:43:50 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n野村發表報告指，內房來港大手投地，加上按揭借貸因素推動樓市，令今年樓價升勢跑羸市場預測，樓價指數至今已升6%。但該行提醒，上述兩大因素的利好效應將於明年減退，料今年樓價上升8%，並將於上半年見頂。<br />\n<br />\n野村指，今年樓市動力主要來自中資、內房高價搶地，但不保證樓價及地價中期前景正面，價格要視乎基本因素。另外，明年按息有上升風險，地產商的二按將會減少。野村表示，在本港經濟基本因素不變的情況下，預期樓價上半年會登頂。"},{"pid":"a3b50f7f1ca7b0d0770f727fa34bf48213589f94","tid":219424,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"搵人打比沈大師問下意見  快!"},{"pid":"2eb7a2e9fe26f57e0e9605e7f4db15341c35c2cd","tid":219424,"uid":24527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44d9fe6ef55a6b38c708a6e257024b2053411fa","tid":219424,"uid":17910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"Lau ming"},{"pid":"7ce048ebaa5614df8278f2533da6dcec3c883be8","tid":219424,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"留名binc"},{"pid":"f3d79ec5fe26390e2e4f88a4b18147009718fca5","tid":219424,"uid":10949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:53:14.000Z","msg":"講到口都臭"},{"pid":"cd9213b887b1c9a41d093d21afb7bc55c3f63c22","tid":219424,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}